OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779304271
OL,3,C30 year search to identify body found
OL,4,Con River Avon bank continues
OL,6,FThe 30 year search to identify the
OL,7,Fbody of a man found dead on the bank
OL,8,Fof the River Avon in Somerset
OL,9,Fcontinues.
OL,11,FThe man was found on May 19, 1996 and
OL,12,Fit is believed he had fallen from
OL,13,FClifton Suspension Bridge.
OL,15,FHe has been described as white, of
OL,16,Fmedium build and was thought to be
OL,17,Faged between 25 and 35 years old.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
