PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779304271
OL,3,C30 year search to identify body found
OL,4,Con River Avon bank continues
OL,6,FHe was approximately 6ft (185cm) tall,
OL,7,Fwith blue eyes. He wore a black
OL,8,Fsweatshirt and jacket, blue 'Lee
OL,9,FRiders' jeans and brown boots.
OL,11,FHe was found with a number of items,
OL,12,Fincluding a photo of his younger self.
OL,14,FIn 2023, volunteer investigators with
OL,15,FLocate International, a charity that
OL,16,Flooks into cold cases of missing and
OL,17,Funidentified people, released a new
OL,18,Fliving depiction of how he would have
OL,19,Flooked in life.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779304271
OL,3,C30 year search to identify body found
OL,4,Con River Avon bank continues
OL,6,FSince the image was released multiple
OL,7,Fpeople have got in contact with the
OL,8,Finvestigators saying they recognise
OL,9,Fthe man shown in the photo, however no
OL,10,Fmatches have been successful.
OL,12,FRoland Hughes, who is the Head of
OL,13,FMedia at Locate International describe
OL,14,Fit as a 'unusual case' due to the fact
OL,15,Fa 'significant' amount of clues were
OL,16,Ffound on him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779304271
OL,3,C30 year search to identify body found
OL,4,Con River Avon bank continues
OL,6,FHe went on to explain how the man was
OL,7,Ffound with a number of books but they
OL,8,Fbelieve he was homeless as he also had
OL,9,Fa sign which said 'sleeping rough
OL,10,Fthank you'.
OL,12,FMark Greenhalgh, Locate
OL,13,FInternational's CEO says: "We will
OL,14,Fcontinue to work on reuniting him with
OL,15,Fhis identity until all possible leads
OL,16,Fare extinguished.
OL,18,F"We are very confident that there are
OL,19,Fplenty of people in and around Bristol
OL,20,F` and possibly elsewhere in the UK `
OL,21,Fwho knew him or may recognise him.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1779304271
OL,3,C30 year search to identify body found
OL,4,Con River Avon bank continues
OL,6,F"His appearance may have changed from
OL,7,Fhis youth, but ask yourself if
OL,8,Fanything about him seems familiar.
OL,10,F"We encourage anyone with any
OL,11,Finformation, however small it may
OL,12,Fappear, to come forward. Even the
OL,13,Fsmallest detail can help take our
OL,14,Finvestigation in a new direction, or
OL,15,Fconfirm something we already believe."
